            <h2>A Cat of Many Colors</h2>
            <p>The Pink Panther wasn't always pink! In his early appearances, he was depicted in various colors,
                including white, gray, and even black. But the pink hue eventually stuck, becoming his signature look
                and a symbol of his playful personality.</p>
            <p>The Pink Panther is known for his love of luxury, good food, and beautiful women. He's also quite the
                prankster, often finding himself in comical chases and scrapes with a bumbling inspector (a character
                inspired by Inspector Clouseau) or other adversaries.</p>
        </section>

